text: Ic eom ligbysig, lace mid <winde,w> <dre> gesomnad, fus forðweges, fyre gemylted, <bear> blowende, byrnende gled.
Ful oft mec gesiþas sendað æfter hondum, þær mec weras ond wif wlonce gecyssað.
Þonne ic mec onhæbbe, hi onhnigað to me, modge miltsum, swa ic mongum sceal ycan upcyme eadignesse.
